### Bug fixes

* Serialize all repodata cache access in a single thread. Open the sharded
  repodata cache (`repodata_shards.db`) in WAL mode with a longer SQLite busy
  timeout. This avoids an issue where the pipelined cache reader thread could
  race with the network writer thread and raise `sqlite3.OperationalError: database is locked`.
  Fall back to the default journal mode on filesystems where WAL is not
  supported. (#924)

